<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <style>
            h1 {
                color: #5e9ca0;
                text-align: center;
            }
        </style>
        <title>Example EJS Email Template</title>
    </head>

    <body>
        <h1>
            Hello, <%= name %>
        </h1>
        <p>We hope this email finds you well!</p>
        <p>We wanted to reach out to let you know about our latest update to our service. Our team has been working hard to
            improve the user experience and make your time with us even better. Thank you for choosing us!</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. We're always here to help.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The <%= company %> Team</p>
    </body>
</html>